snippet: Christine C. Quinn, the City Council speaker, leads her Democratic mayoral rivals with a war chest of almost $5.6 million, according to financial-disclosure reports released on Friday.
abstract: Financial-disclosure reports show that New York City Council Speaker Christine C Quinn leads her Democratic rivals in mayor's race with a war chest of almost $5.6 million.
lead_paragraph: Christine C. Quinn, the City Council speaker, leads her Democratic mayoral rivals with a war chest of almost $5.6 million, according to financial-disclosure reports released on Friday.

headline.seo: Quinn Leads Democrats in Fund-Raising for Mayoral Race
headline.main: Quinn Leads Democrats in Fund-Raising for 2013 Campaign
